game_description: Online VR gym experience. Navigate around a virtual gym to learn about gym equipment, énergie fitness clubs and how to workout. Great for first time gym users to get a feel of the gym from the comfort of your own home or for experienced gym users who want to utilise tech to expand their gym knowledge.
review_1: A charming environment that seems to be a recreation of a real place, who knows.
review_2: Its just like visiting the gym and really educational!
